{"tid":2364313,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"如果返工屙屎，俾你撞破隔離格同事借屙屎偷懶，你會唔會去篤灰？","createTime":"2021-01-13T01:44:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T02:14:04.000Z","uid":40930,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16c951ca15da0bc05a39057f7adc49761f85b27c","tid":2364313,"uid":40930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T01:44:15.000Z","msg":"返工去廁所，大家目標都一致<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係點知有日坐你隔離個隔同你一樣坐咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲周不時笑到gap gap 聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/what.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你會？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n篤灰？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要屙得長久，唔止係個日，仲要係日日個隻，一定要keep 住win-win 嘅狀態先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都知道，是但有一方背叛咗嘅，傻鳩boss肯肯定會話咩以後大家都冇得去屙屎之煩廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，不妨有時大家齊齊屙夠出去時俾對方一個微笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁大家就會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/awake.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a435ab688797b9e28e7fb282c6fdbb13060f94","tid":2364313,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T01:53:51.000Z","msg":"內容豐富💯"},{"pid":"613134bd1e670069fcf2cc644a18999b6a89d4f7","tid":2364313,"uid":33694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T02:26:55.000Z","msg":"屙屎唔俾笑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872fba380d2870810e607ae715cc64969480408c","tid":2364313,"uid":345353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T04:30:46.000Z","msg":"盡量係姐姐洗完廁所果陣入去訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa9478349e1d5390e77897154d3430e02c0bc62","tid":23643